              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-3 border-b border-slate-200">
                <div>
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-terracotta">Taverna Stolis</h4>
                    <p class="text-slate-gray">Comida tradicional griega y albanesa en un ambiente familiar.</p>
                </div>
                <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Taverna+Stolis" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-terracotta font-semibold hover:underline whitespace-nowrap ml-4">
